snippet.title: GTA Alien City Mod Gameplay (+Download)
snippet.description:
GTA Alien City (Anderius) Gameplay, recorded in high definition. 
DOWNLOAD LINK: http://www.gta-modding.com/area/index.php?act=view&id=770

A montage of gameplay clips from GTA Alien City, a total conversion mod for GTA San Andreas. This mod replaces the original map with a new city, vehicles and a brand new storyline. Currently this mod is only available in Russian and no subtitles for any other language have been released.

Music: 
Malcolm Kirby Jr. - Keymaster (Saints Row IV Soundtrack)

● Platform: Windows PC
● Recorded using FRAPS Verision 3.5.9
● Edited using Adobe Premiere Pro CS6

Stay Connected:
